snippet.textDisplay: I am all for experiments and fusions. That being said, essence of this song is Pushto music and inclusion of a hardcore Pushtun singer (Humayoon Khan or Bakhtiyar Khattak or even Shaan) with better pronunciation than Faakhir along with a Traditional Rubab player (like Farhan Bogra) would have made it a better song. Nonetheless super effort. Thumbs Up from Qatar.
snippet.textOriginal: I am all for experiments and fusions. That being said, essence of this song is Pushto music and inclusion of a hardcore Pushtun singer (Humayoon Khan or Bakhtiyar Khattak or even Shaan) with better pronunciation than Faakhir along with a Traditional Rubab player (like Farhan Bogra) would have made it a better song. Nonetheless super effort. Thumbs Up from Qatar.
